    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 5,200₽ | 物品价值: 5,200 | Mechanic报价: 2,912₽.50 BMG（12.7x99 毫米勃朗宁机枪弹）M903 SLAP 脱壳穿甲弹。该款弹药采用 7.62 毫米口径的穿甲弹头作为弹芯，外覆聚合物材质弹托，出膛后弹托脱落，确保弹芯部分获得足够的初速与穿甲能力。该款弹药的停止作用相当惊人，一旦命中目标能够造成巨量伤害。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 5,200₽ | 物品价值: 5,200 | Mechanic报价: 2,912₽A .50 BMG (12.7x99mm NATO) M903 SLAP (Saboted Light Armor Penetrator) cartridge. Created by placing a 7.62 armor-piercing bullet in a polymer container that separates after leaving the barrel. The cartridge has significant stopping power and is capable of inflicting devastating damage to the target upon impact."
    },
